jQuery HTMLbuilder plugin. ("$.fn.buildin")

1 or 2 parameters accepted:
 * 1:  $(selector).buildin([<HTMLbuilder array>])
       e.g. $('p').buildin(['a',{href:'#cool'},'This is so easy!'])

 * 2:  $(selector).buildin("<jquery insertion fn>", [<HTMLbuilder array>])
       e.g. $('p').buildin('prepend', ['a',{href:'#cool'},'This is so easy!'])